I have not written anything close to a serious entry in some time but for some reason I get the inclination to make up for this today and write a little.

I suppose I should start by saying that about 3 weeks ago I went to the docs and got meself of Anti depressants ..... this is a very hard thing for me to do as last time i tried them they turned me into a raging psycho and I lost everything I had because of them....

Anyway that was a long time ago and I am happy to report that so far so good and I am feeling tons better already :)

I have been spending a lot of time with Clairy over the last few months and I must say that it has helped me realise many thingasabout myself.

I am currently living at a friends housie and that in itself is not an ideal situation that is causing back aches ( sleeping on le sofa ) and just general crowdy stress with very little time to myself.

The idea was to move into a friends housie and save myself money to save for my move to bridgwater ...... it is not going to plan and i dont feel any closer what so ever to my goal


HELP ME I NEED MOTIVATION!!!!!!

anyway apart from that all is sweet funkyness in le life of Marl

Had a super Fab time with Clairy this week ..... we had ooodles and poodles of fun!!!!!

I got ganged up on by Clairy and Kay but I think i held my own quite well :P

 

Thankies to Clairy for the fab new desktop that she made for me ...... she is erm sooo thoughtful!

 

I did threaten to post some of the more embarrasing clairy pics on here but I will be all nice and leave them snug on my hard drive ....... though if anyone wants to see then let me know ...... and shhhhhh dont tell Clairy :p

Finally got my arse into gear... YAY!

 

with a little of encouragement ... ok maybe alot I have finally made some steps towards moving to Somerset. My landlord has been given 1 months notice and I shall be staying with a friend for a couple of months so I can get a little saving underway.

There is so much shite going on with my family atm and I really cannot wait to get as far away from it all as possible.

Now all I need to do is get through the next 2 months here and try find a job and somewhere to live in Somerset. I am quite confident that It is not going to be too difficult as long as I can stay focused.

I hate my job and my entire life here which is really helping me keep on the right track and plenty of support from my friends

 

ok that will do for now as I am just talking a load of jumbled pooness

Well it is about time I wrote something in my infernal journal and seeing as i am currently bored out of my mind this seems like a great time.

It has been a rollercoaster of a month for me but I can still say I do not regret one moment. Emotionally I suppose I am a tad unstable and I have done some rather dumb stuff over the past few days but you can only learn from your actions and that could only be a good thing.

I at this time want to just thank Clairy for being there for me. you are my rock and the only person I know I can confide in.

I am proud to have you in my life, you are a damn fine bitch !!

I shall be moving to smelly Bridgwater in the coming months, I really need to start a new life as I am so unhappy with the one I have created for myself here, And I cant wait to hang around with Clairy :)

 

Anyway that will do for this entry ... i really need to make more of an effort!

How tiring was that.... In my infinite wisdom I offered to cook xmas dinner for me family .... what I did not know was that the oven had broken down and I would have to cook for 8 people using just a combination microwave oven. I started cooking at 06:30 and finaly dished up the food at 17:00.

 All in all though I had a pretty funky xmas made special by someone very important to me :) ( it is quite amazing the effect just a few texts and phone calls can have on a person)

I hope everyone had a great xmas though i have to admit I am pretty much glad it is all over. Now I just need to get new years out of the way and I can start dealing with all my new future plans :)

Think i might be turning into a sex crazed mad man.... I really need to get this under control or i might just go blind lol
http://delerius.livejournal.com/4414.html
Wishing everyone on LJ a very Merry Xmas and an even better new year full of fun and stuff  :)

I am kinda fed up with walking around with a cloudy head ... why cant everything just make sense?

20 Years Ago, I . . .

1. Was bullied at school
2. was abused
3. was very shy

 

15 Years Ago, I . . .

1. Had a great group of friends
2. became a little more confident
3. Was taking my GCSE's


10 Years Ago, I...

1. Was wrapped up in work
2. Was depressed
3. Had a fit body :)


5 Years Ago, I...

1. Left the mother of my kids and was living in Scotland
2. Was wrongly accused of a very serious crime
3. was very unhappily in a relationship
4. worked as a travel agent

3 Years Ago, I...

1. Spent lots of time in Los Angeles
2. Loved someone more than i thought possible at the time
3. Was very depressed being so far away from her
4. was covered in human bites and scratches

1 Year Ago, I...

1. Was living with my then-Girlfriend in Bracknell
2. Suffered from depression and refused to acknowledge it.
3. was introduced to the black sheep bar and love it
4. lost touch with most of my online friends

So far this year, I...

1. Lost someone I loved
2. Moved house to shared one full of nutters
3. learnt to accept who I am and that it is really not so bad
4. Been the most depressed and the most happy I have ever been
5. renewed a very important friendship
6. Was honest with myself for the first time
7. Made some HUGE mistakes in the women dept

Yesterday, I...

1. Spent the Day with Clairy
2. Realise many things I need or need to change in my life
3. travelled home ala train
4. had one of the best days I can remember for a very long time

Today, I...

1. Went to work
3. Started reading a book Clairy bought me yesterday
4. Sat online with no one to talk to
5. Started making new jobness enquiries

Tomorrow, I...

1. am going to work again :(
2. Will try to have a fun filled fluffy day
3. will spend the afternoon with my kiddies
4. Will probably spend too much time online... again

Well today was kinda mooooo

I think the concept of going to work after 2 days off has sunk me into a minor dose of pissiness.

had a good morning though ....... cant wait to hear Clairy singing Conte Partiro ..... I am gonna laugh my ass off .... well as soon as she has finished laughing at me anyway.

seen the funniest thing EVER today.

I saw an old episode of Rainbow .... and I can honestly say that I do not ever remember quite as much sexual innuendo ..... infact i swear they prolly would not show that episode til after the watershed nowadays hehe

feel a bit bad that I have got so disorganized that i am reduced to begging to parents and friends to feed me lol.... but I have learned my lesson now and it will not be happening again in a hurry.

Gave prolly my first and last non sexual massage today ..... it was not half as much fun..... tis far more fun to relax the poor lady then ruin it by jumping her hehe...... but she is not my type so i will reserve them for yummilicious ladies lol.

Well I suppose I should get my first entry out of the way.

Been using Diaryland but a friend has informed me just how funky this place is so only fair I at least give it a go

I am not going to make this entry all poosie and depressed as I have plenty of time to put some of those in.

Had a very busy week of 12hr shifts and I am a wee bit tired, but all in all I have had a truly funky if not a little odd week

firstly I have started talking to the funkiest girlie I know again (clairybo) .... I missed her more than I miss a kebab on a weekend

My best friend Is getting married so I get to spend lots of time talking him out of it and even better I will get to tell him " I told you so " when it all falls to pieces

I got an interview date for a much better paid job with oooodles of holiday entitlement.

I finally managed to pick up a book and start reading ..... yay

there is prolly loads more I could mention this week but I am way too sleepy to think


Oh and I am super pissy cos once I have finished this entry and I look at it, I am gonna see a very poosie unsparkly entry that needs to look colourful

Clairy HEEELLLLPPPP MEEEEEEE
